Viewers Note: The following list is a 2007 independent reading of Prospect Cemetery and includes other submitted interments listed elsewhere on this website. You may view the other listing by clicking HERE.

Contributors Note: An interesting note about Prospect Cemetery: In 1988 there had been approx. 12700 burials but only about 7000 of those burials had grave stones to mark their last resting place. -- "ME"
